text: Briana Evigan (born October 28, 1986) is an American dancer and actress. In Step Up and its sequels, she played Andie West. She also played Annette in the movie Mother's Day. Briana Evigan was born in Los Angeles. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:1986 births Category:Living people
